Catherine Steadman https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Catherine_Steadman 0 Catherine Steadman (born February 8, 1987) is an English actress and author, best known for playing Mabel Lane Fox in series 5 (2014) of ITV drama Downton Abbey. Her debut novel, the psychological thriller, Something in the Water was published in June 2018 by Simon Schuster UK and Penguin Random House USA.
